These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, dunhill
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
2 different games are played: bridge, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, july
1. the game-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Cigar       | dunhill       | game |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Game       | monopoly    | bridge    |
| Birthday   | july       | september      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, lavender
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer
2 different games are played: snooker, monopoly
City: hamburg, miami
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Color      | lavender     | brown |
| Job           | entrepreneur | lawyer      |
| Game   | monopoly  | snooker      |
| City         | hamburg | miami     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, rowing
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, software-developer
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, grey
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the designer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Sport      | baseball | rowing  |
| Job          | designer    | software-developer   |
| Color   | grey  | fuchsia   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, march
2 different games are played: backgammon, canasta
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, old-henry
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
2. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Birthday      | june       | march |
| Game          | canasta         | backgammon    |
| Cigar           | old-henry | siglo    |
| Music-Genre   | punk           | techno   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-5::.
