1. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the palace house is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| House         | cottage | palace   |
| Flower   | daisy | lily       |
| City         | new-york   | london |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike     |

