.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-9::.
2 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, montecristo
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, apricot
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Pet   | fish         | hedgehog    |
| Cigar       | montecristo     | cain  |
| Hobby      | board-games | chess     |
| Color        | apricot     | emerald |

