.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, pall-mall
There 2 different types of food: garlic, cauliflower
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, board-games
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Cigar           | pall-mall | dunhill     |
| Food   | garlic          | cauliflower |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Hobby     | board-games            | drawing       |

 